---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Community Impact"
  description="Weyland-Yutani Corporation community impact programs. Explorers Academy education, veteran employment, Olympic partnership, colony development, healthcare access, and employee volunteerism."
>
  <Header />

  <main class="bg-black pt-36">
    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden border-b-4 border-[#FFC600]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-20"></div>
      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute top-0 left-0 right-0"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 text-center py-24">
        <div class="inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-[#FFC600] text-black font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 clip-corner">
          SUSTAINABILITY
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-black text-white mb-8 leading-none uppercase">
          COMMUNITY <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">IMPACT</span>
        </h1>

        <div class="h-1 w-64 bg-[#FFC600] mx-auto mb-8"></div>

        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto uppercase tracking-wide font-mono">
          CORPORATE SUCCESS MEANS NOTHING IF IT DOES NOT TRANSLATE INTO GENUINE BENEFIT FOR THE COMMUNITIES WE SERVE,
          ON EARTH AND ACROSS THE STARS.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="hazard-stripes h-3 absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- IMPACT AT A GLANCE -->
    <section class="relative py-16 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">$5B+</div>
            <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase mt-2">EDUCATION INVESTMENT</div>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">250K</div>
            <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase mt-2">STUDENTS ENROLLED</div>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">50K+</div>
            <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase mt-2">VETERANS EMPLOYED</div>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">1.2M</div>
            <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase mt-2">VOLUNTEER HOURS</div>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">300+</div>
            <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase mt-2">COMMUNITIES SERVED</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- EDUCATION -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">EDUCATION</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            EXPLORERS ACADEMY & <span class="text-[#FFC600]">LITTLE EXPLORERS</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-4">EXPLORERS ACADEMY</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              FOUNDED IN 2025, THE EXPLORERS ACADEMY IS THE LARGEST PRIVATE STEM EDUCATION INITIATIVE IN HISTORY. OPERATING ON EVERY CONTINENT AND ON LUNA, THE ACADEMY PROVIDES WORLD-CLASS EDUCATION TO STUDENTS FROM UNDERSERVED COMMUNITIES WHO OTHERWISE WOULD NOT HAVE ACCESS TO ADVANCED SCIENCE AND ENGINEERING PROGRAMS.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">8 CAMPUSES ON EARTH, 1 ON LUNA</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">250,000+ STUDENTS CURRENTLY ENROLLED</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">94% GRADUATE EMPLOYMENT RATE</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">15,000+ CORPORATE MENTORS</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="mt-6">
              <a href="/careers/explorers-academy" class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider hover:text-white transition-colors">LEARN MORE &rarr;</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-4">LITTLE EXPLORERS FUND</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
              THE LITTLE EXPLORERS FUND IS OUR DEDICATED PHILANTHROPY VEHICLE FOR EDUCATION. WITH OVER $5 BILLION DONATED TO DATE, THE FUND SUPPORTS SCHOLARSHIPS, INFRASTRUCTURE, AND OUTREACH PROGRAMS THAT EXTEND FAR BEYOND OUR OWN ACADEMY CAMPUSES, REACHING PUBLIC SCHOOLS AND COMMUNITY ORGANIZATIONS WORLDWIDE.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">$5B+ IN TOTAL DONATIONS</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">50,000 FULL-RIDE SCHOLARSHIPS PER YEAR</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">STEM LAB GRANTS TO 2,000+ PUBLIC SCHOOLS</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">COMMUNITY SCIENCE CENTERS IN 40 COUNTRIES</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- OLYMPICS -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-black border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">WORLD PARTNERSHIP</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            OLYMPIC <span class="text-[#FFC600]">PARTNERSHIP</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="corp-card p-8 md:p-12">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
            <div>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
                WEYLAND-YUTANI IS A WORLD OLYMPIC PARTNER FOR THE PERIOD 2071-2091, THE LONGEST SPONSORSHIP COMMITMENT IN OLYMPIC HISTORY. OUR PARTNERSHIP SUPPORTS ATHLETES FROM EVERY NATION ON EARTH AND, FOR THE FIRST TIME, COLONIAL TERRITORIES.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
                WE PROVIDE TECHNOLOGICAL SUPPORT INCLUDING MEDPOD MEDICAL SERVICES FOR ATHLETES, HOLOGRAPHIC BROADCAST SYSTEMS FOR GLOBAL COVERAGE, AND SUSTAINABLE VENUE INFRASTRUCTURE LEVERAGING OUR CONSTRUCTION AND ENERGY EXPERTISE.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed">
                THE PARTNERSHIP ALSO FUNDS THE W-Y OLYMPIC SCHOLARSHIP PROGRAM, SUPPORTING 5,000 YOUNG ATHLETES FROM UNDERSERVED COMMUNITIES IN PURSUING THEIR SPORTING AND ACADEMIC GOALS.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
                <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">2071-2091</div>
                <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase mt-2">PARTNERSHIP PERIOD</div>
              </div>
              <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
                <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">20</div>
                <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase mt-2">YEARS OF COMMITMENT</div>
              </div>
              <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
                <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">5,000</div>
                <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase mt-2">ATHLETE SCHOLARSHIPS</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- VETERANS -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">EMPLOYMENT</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            VETERAN <span class="text-[#FFC600]">PROGRAMS</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="corp-card p-8 md:p-12">
          <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-8">
            WEYLAND-YUTANI IS THE CHIEF EMPLOYER OF ASIAN CONFLICT VETERANS, WITH 35% OF ALL TRANSITIONING SERVICE MEMBERS CHOOSING OUR COMPANY IN 2038. OUR COMPREHENSIVE VETERAN TRANSITION PROGRAMS SET THE INDUSTRY STANDARD FOR SUPPORTING MILITARY PROFESSIONALS AS THEY ENTER CORPORATE CAREERS.
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-black p-6 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-black text-[#FFC600]">50,000+</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase mt-2">VETERAN EMPLOYEES</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-black p-6 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-black text-[#FFC600]">35%</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase mt-2">TRANSITION COHORT HIRING</div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-black p-6 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-black text-[#FFC600]">TOP 10</div>
              <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase mt-2">BEST EMPLOYER FOR VETERANS</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center mt-8">
            <a href="/careers/veterans" class="text-[#FFC600] font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider hover:text-white transition-colors">VETERAN PROGRAM DETAILS &rarr;</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- COLONY DEVELOPMENT -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-black border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">COLONY COMMUNITIES</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            COLONY COMMUNITY <span class="text-[#FFC600]">DEVELOPMENT</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">INFRASTRUCTURE</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">
              EVERY W-Y COLONY RECEIVES COMPREHENSIVE COMMUNITY INFRASTRUCTURE INCLUDING SCHOOLS, HEALTHCARE FACILITIES, RECREATION CENTERS, AND PLACES OF WORSHIP. WE BUILD COMMUNITIES, NOT JUST OUTPOSTS.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">GOVERNANCE SUPPORT</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">
              WE SUPPORT THE TRANSITION FROM CORPORATE ADMINISTRATION TO SELF-GOVERNANCE AS COLONIES MATURE. OUR CIVIC DEVELOPMENT PROGRAMS TRAIN LOCAL LEADERS AND BUILD DEMOCRATIC INSTITUTIONS.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase">ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">
              SMALL BUSINESS GRANTS, ENTREPRENEURSHIP TRAINING, AND LOCAL PROCUREMENT POLICIES ENSURE THAT COLONY ECONOMIES DEVELOP INDEPENDENTLY AND ARE NOT SOLELY DEPENDENT ON CORPORATE OPERATIONS.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- HEALTHCARE ACCESS -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a] border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">HEALTH SCIENCES</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            HEALTHCARE <span class="text-[#FFC600]">ACCESS</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-4">MEDPOD GLOBAL ACCESS INITIATIVE</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
              OUR GLOBAL ACCESS INITIATIVE DEPLOYS MEDPOD AUTONOMOUS SURGICAL SYSTEMS TO UNDERSERVED COMMUNITIES ON EARTH AND ACROSS THE COLONIAL NETWORK. BY REDUCING THE NEED FOR SPECIALIST SURGEONS, MEDPOD TECHNOLOGY BRINGS ADVANCED HEALTHCARE TO REGIONS THAT HAVE NEVER HAD ACCESS TO IT.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">12,000 MEDPODS DEPLOYED TO UNDERSERVED AREAS</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">3.2 MILLION PROCEDURES PERFORMED</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">99.7% SUCCESS RATE</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">42 JURISDICTIONS WITH FULL REGULATORY APPROVAL</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="corp-card p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-black text-white mb-4 uppercase border-b border-[#1a1a1a] pb-4">COLONY HEALTHCARE STANDARD</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed mb-4">
              EVERY COLONY IN THE W-Y NETWORK IS EQUIPPED WITH HEALTHCARE INFRASTRUCTURE MEETING OR EXCEEDING EARTH-STANDARD REQUIREMENTS. OUR COLONY HEALTHCARE STANDARD ENSURES THAT GEOGRAPHIC DISTANCE FROM EARTH DOES NOT MEAN REDUCED QUALITY OF CARE.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">MEDPOD INSTALLATION IN ALL COLONIES (1,000+ POP)</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">TRAINED MEDICAL STAFF AT EVERY FACILITY</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">TELEMEDICINE LINKS TO EARTH VIA FTL RELAY</li>
              <li class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase status-active">PREVENTIVE CARE AND WELLNESS PROGRAMS</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CULTURAL PRESERVATION -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-black border-b-2 border-[#1a1a1a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">HERITAGE</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            CULTURAL <span class="text-[#FFC600]">PRESERVATION</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="corp-card p-8 md:p-12">
          <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-8">
            AS HUMANITY EXPANDS ACROSS THE STARS, PRESERVING THE CULTURAL HERITAGE THAT DEFINES US BECOMES EVER MORE IMPORTANT. WEYLAND-YUTANI'S CULTURAL PRESERVATION INITIATIVE ENSURES THAT THE DIVERSITY OF HUMAN CULTURE IS CARRIED FORWARD TO EVERY COLONY WE ESTABLISH.
          </p>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-black p-6 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <h4 class="text-white font-black text-sm uppercase mb-3">DIGITAL HERITAGE ARCHIVE</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">THE LARGEST DIGITAL REPOSITORY OF HUMAN CULTURAL ARTIFACTS, DISTRIBUTED ACROSS ALL MAJOR COLONIES. ART, LITERATURE, MUSIC, AND HISTORICAL RECORDS PRESERVED FOR FUTURE GENERATIONS.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-black p-6 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <h4 class="text-white font-black text-sm uppercase mb-3">COLONY CULTURAL CENTERS</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">EVERY COLONY WITH A POPULATION EXCEEDING 5,000 RECEIVES A DEDICATED CULTURAL CENTER, OFFERING COMMUNITY GATHERING SPACE, EDUCATION, AND PRESERVATION OF LOCAL AND TERRESTRIAL TRADITIONS.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-black p-6 border border-[#1a1a1a] clip-corner">
              <h4 class="text-white font-black text-sm uppercase mb-3">INDIGENOUS PARTNERSHIP</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs uppercase leading-relaxed">PARTNERSHIP PROGRAMS WITH INDIGENOUS COMMUNITIES ON EARTH TO PRESERVE LANGUAGE, TRADITION, AND KNOWLEDGE SYSTEMS, ENSURING THESE INVALUABLE PERSPECTIVES INFORM HUMANITY'S EXPANSION.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- VOLUNTEERISM -->
    <section class="relative py-24 bg-[#0a0a0a]">
      <div class="industrial-grid-dense absolute inset-0 opacity-10"></div>

      <div class="relative container mx-auto px-6 max-w-5xl">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="text-[#FFC600] text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono">OUR PEOPLE</span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mt-4 uppercase">
            EMPLOYEE <span class="text-[#FFC600]">VOLUNTEERISM</span>
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="corp-card p-8 md:p-12">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
            <div>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed mb-6">
                EVERY WEYLAND-YUTANI EMPLOYEE RECEIVES 40 HOURS OF PAID VOLUNTEER TIME ANNUALLY. OUR EMPLOYEES CONTRIBUTE THEIR SKILLS AND TIME TO CAUSES THAT MATTER, FROM MENTORING ACADEMY STUDENTS TO BUILDING COMMUNITY INFRASTRUCTURE ON COLONY WORLDS.
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-400 font-mono text-sm uppercase leading-relaxed">
                THE CORPORATE MATCHING PROGRAM DOUBLES EVERY DOLLAR DONATED BY AN EMPLOYEE TO QUALIFIED CHARITABLE ORGANIZATIONS, WITH NO ANNUAL CAP. IN FY2058, OUR EMPLOYEES DONATED $340 MILLION IN PERSONAL CONTRIBUTIONS, MATCHED BY THE CORPORATION FOR A COMBINED IMPACT OF $680 MILLION.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
                <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">1.2M</div>
                <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase mt-2">VOLUNTEER HOURS LOGGED</div>
                <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase">FY2058</div>
              </div>
              <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
                <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">$680M</div>
                <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase mt-2">COMBINED GIVING</div>
                <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase">EMPLOYEE + MATCH</div>
              </div>
              <div class="corp-card p-6 text-center">
                <div class="text-3xl font-black text-[#FFC600] text-glow-yellow">78%</div>
                <div class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase mt-2">EMPLOYEE PARTICIPATION</div>
                <div class="text-gray-600 font-mono text-xs uppercase">IN VOLUNTEER PROGRAMS</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-16">
          <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
            <a href="/sustainability" class="btn-primary text-sm">SUSTAINABILITY OVERVIEW</a>
            <a href="/sustainability/terraforming-impact" class="btn-secondary text-sm">TERRAFORMING IMPACT</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .clip-corner {
    clip-path: polygon(8px 0, 100% 0, 100% calc(100% - 8px), calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0 100%, 0 8px);
  }
</style>
